    "draft": false,
    "deleted": false,
    "published": "Sat Apr 18th 2020, 6:07 PM",
    "html": "<p>I continued working on <a href=\"http://news.catpea.com\">news.catpea.com</a> and actually made very good progress.</p>\n<p>I wanted to pull the poems out of code and give them an alternate version that can be easily read via github.</p>\n<p>Here is the <a href=\"https://github.com/fantasyui-com/news-catpea-com/blob/17041ee955dacdf17c1f5f7c706bd1bbbd8b3060/db/content/posts/aquamarine-sandybrown.md\">result</a>, it is not pretty, but it is pretty readable.</p>\n<p>Now I can continue with making <a href=\"http://news.catpea.com\">news.catpea.com</a> look nicer, I am missing some icons, and i want to allow browsing by category (research/quarantine) so that with a click only poems will come up.</p>\n"
