    "published": "Thu Apr 9th 2020, 6:07 PM",
    "html": "<p>Yay, Night Mode seems to have worked out, I even gave it nice and tidy animation. <a href=\"https://octicons.github.com/\">Octicons</a> had a light bulb icon for me so it all went smoothly. Give it a try, go to the <a href=\"/research\">Research</a> page, put on some shades, and click on the <img class=\"img-fluid rounded shadow mt-5 mb-2\" src=\"icons/light-bulb.svg\" alt=\"\"> icon .</p>\n<p><img class=\"img-fluid rounded shadow mt-5 mb-2\" src=\"research/bulb.png\" alt=\"Night Mode Toggle\"></p>\n<p>Night Mode Toggle</p>\n"
