    "published": "Tue Mar 24th 2020, 5:11 PM",
    "html": "<p>Captain&#39;s Log Supplemental: Day Eight and Half... of Quarantine. I almost finished eating my 30 day supply of Chicken, my muscles have tripled in size, and I have the strength of 300. I begun releasing a New Album entitled <strong>THE WARRIOR</strong> Inspired by <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/results?search_query=Tron+Legacy\">TRON</a> and <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mVxLhy1v-xU\">LOFI Hip-Hop</a>.</p>\n"
